column14: X1 = Finished area of residence (sq. ft.)
X2 = Number of bedrooms in residence
X3 = Number of bathrooms in residence
X4 = Presence of air conditioning: 1 = yes; 0 = no
X5 = Number of cars that garage will hold
X6 = Presence of swimming pool: 1 = yes; 0 = no
X7 = Year property was originally constructed
X8 = Constuction quality: 1 = hi; 2 = medium; 3 = lo
A city tax assessor was interested in predicting residential home sales prices in a midwestern
city as a function of various charateristics of the home and surrouding property.
Data were obtained at home sales during the year 2002.
